{"tid":141283,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"致高登打手／五毛同埋最低賤既早洩","createTime":"2017-03-02T19:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T15:46:45.000Z","uid":17510,"like":51,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c20593fb469866f13b4660ee206bc4f9528a2759","tid":141283,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:11:34.000Z","msg":"估唔到早洩到今時今日都仲係咁不知悔改<br />\n向到縱容你班手下胡作非為<br />\n<br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<br />\n我地絕對相信連巴唔似得早洩咁卑鄙無恥<br />\n<br />\n老老實實  如果你肯一早為BAM HKG+而公開地躹躬道歉<br />\n根本就唔會搞到今時今日咁樣既局面<br />\n<br />\n到左今日高登再無高登仔係閣下咎由自取<br />\n你以為打殘LIHKG我地就會返返去你個垃圾高登只係你夢心妄想<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月出得第一個LIHKG  <br />\n我地就有本事可以再出得到千千萬萬個LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都無謂<br />\n我地對連尼住同望遠兩位巴打係無條件信任<br />\n當中既情義係你依啲反覆無常既小人唔會明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之一句到尾<br />\n我就點都撐LIHKG"},{"pid":"fb00cec81152aea4344121de96cba5ec351eb9bf","tid":141283,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T20:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e4c6d3af0d1249fc5b0667e1bdcd7d42b9c98a","tid":141283,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e8ae44e56b2b64c37a9cde6edda396885b53ab","tid":141283,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2531ef7487cec7206532af667b46854e3815a222","tid":141283,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"2隻高登仔偷偷負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68a75a8ada478a0bfd7fdca723b34feeb25f252","tid":141283,"uid":18706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"其實由佢亂鳩bam人開始已經冇撚上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />